Welcome back to China Uncensored.

5
00:00:14,390 --> 00:00:15,440
I’m Chris Chappell.

6
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:18,940
You know, I criticize the Chinese Communist
Party.

7
00:00:18,940 --> 00:00:20,320
A lot.

8
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:22,560
